Source: ttf-dejavu
Section: fonts
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Nick Black <nick.black@sprezzatech.com>
XSBC-Original-Maintainer: Debian Fonts Task Force <pkg-fonts-devel@lists.alioth.debian.org>
Build-Depends: cdbs (>= 0.4.46), debhelper (>= 5.0.42)
Build-Depends-Indep: fontforge-nox | fontforge, perl, libfont-ttf-perl (>= 0.35)
Standards-Version: 3.9.4
Vcs-Svn: svn://svn.debian.org/pkg-fonts/packages/ttf-dejavu/trunk
